<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head>
    <title>CSS Text Test: tab-size: 4</title>
    <link href="david@openweb.io" rel="author" title="David Storey" />
    <style type="text/css">
        .container {
            position: absolute;
        }
        .green {
            position: absolute; 
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background: green;
         }
        .red {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background: red;
            tab-size: 4;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>The test passes if there is no red.</p>
    <div class="container">
        <pre class="green">    </pre>
    </div>

</body></html>